<body xmlns="http://www.w3.org/ns/ttml" xmlns:tts="http://www.w3.org/ns/ttml#styling" tts:textAlign="center">
    <div>
      <p begin="00:00:30,597" end="00:00:34,582">&#65279;&#9834; [Music] &#9834;</p>
      <p begin="00:00:47,142" end="00:00:50,384">$$ Year 6 of the AIDS epidemic. </p>
      <p begin="00:00:54,784" end="00:00:59,556">$$ Greenwich Village, New York City.<br xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"/>The epicenter. </p>
      <p begin="00:01:07,092" end="00:01:12,569">$$ With no drugs to treat the disease,<br xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"/>AIDS is nearly 100% fatal. </p>
      <p begin="00:01:12,569" end="00:01:16,446">$$ Panic drives a backlash<br xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"/>of blame and anti-gay violence. </p>
      <p begin="00:01:16,446" end="00:01:19,323">$$ Even hospitals<br xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"/>routinely turn away the dying. </p>
      <p begin="00:01:26,127" end="00:01:28,791">$$ Fighting for their lives,<br xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"/>patients and their advocates </p>
      <p begin="00:01:28,791" end="00:01:30,993">$$ take matters into their own hands. </p>
      <p begin="00:01:31,627" end="00:01:34,407">- Welcome to ACT UP. We are <br xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"/>the AIDS Coalition</p>
      <p begin="00:01:34,407" end="00:01:36,638">- [together] to unleash power.</p>
      <p begin="00:01:36,638" end="00:01:40,052">A diverse, non-partisan group<br xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"/>and individuals united in anger</p>
      <p begin="00:01:40,052" end="00:01:42,105">and committed to direct action</p>
      <p begin="00:01:42,105" end="00:01:44,130">-[together] to end the AIDS crisis.</p>
      <p begin="00:01:44,130" end="00:01:51,674">- In less than 12 hours from now,<br xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"/>we are gonna be taking over City Hall.</p>
      <p begin="00:01:51,966" end="00:01:54,123">[Applause]</p>
      <p begin="00:01:54,123" end="00:01:55,843">[Crowd chanting]</p>
      <p begin="00:01:55,843" end="00:01:58,111">- [Ed Koch] Yes.<br xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"/>- [male reporter] Mr. Mayor,</p>
      <p begin="00:01:58,111" end="00:01:59,280">in campaigning <br xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"/>for the lesbian and gay vote,</p>
      <p begin="00:01:59,280" end="00:02:02,084">in an election year, a bit of<br xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"/>historical context is necessary</p>
      <p begin="00:02:02,084" end="00:02:04,184">in dealing with the AIDS crisis<br xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"/>in New York City.</p>
      <p begin="00:02:04,184" end="00:02:06,238">It wasn't until 1983 that you met</p>
      <p begin="00:02:06,238" end="00:02:08,306">with people to deal with<br xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"/>the AIDS crisis.</p>
      <p begin="00:02:08,306" end="00:02:09,513">How do you respond to these questions?</p>
      <p begin="00:02:09,513" end="00:02:10,690">- [Ed] That it's a falsehood.</p>
      <p begin="00:02:10,690" end="00:02:13,446">- Please, anybody who's<br xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"/>thinking about being arrested,</p>
      <p begin="00:02:13,446" end="00:02:17,982">
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">fill out a support sheet, make sure<br/>your support person knows who you are</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="00:02:18,028" end="00:02:20,235">and what group you're in.<br xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"/>Yeah?</p>
      <p begin="00:02:20,404" end="00:02:25,894">- Um, if we end up in The Tombs,<br xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"/>is there like a queer tank there</p>
      <p begin="00:02:25,894" end="00:02:28,897">and would you recommend that we<br xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"/>ask to be there?</p>
      <p begin="00:02:28,897" end="00:02:31,484">- There is a homo tank<br xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"/>and I've been there</p>
      <p begin="00:02:31,484" end="00:02:33,834">and it's better than the straight tank,<br xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"/>let me tell you.</p>
      <p begin="00:02:33,834" end="00:02:35,000">- [Ed] Who else? Yes?</p>
      <p begin="00:02:35,000" end="00:02:38,663">- [reporter] In the past,<br xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"/>you've described ACT UP as fascist</p>
      <p begin="00:02:38,663" end="00:02:40,736">yet in the press release, <br xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"/>you called them concerned citizen.</p>
      <p begin="00:02:40,736" end="00:02:43,215">
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">I was wondering <br/>what changed your mind?</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="00:02:43,215" end="00:02:45,815">- [Ed] I don't think <br xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"/>that you can't use both.</p>
      <p begin="00:02:45,815" end="00:02:48,571">Fascist can be concerned citizens.</p>
      <p begin="00:02:49,709" end="00:02:55,882">And I don't believe they are fascist.<br xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"/>I think they have used the fascist tactic.</p>
      <p begin="00:02:55,882" end="00:03:00,336">- Let us celebrate together<br xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"/>tonight, the end of the last day</p>
      <p begin="00:03:00,336" end="00:03:02,646">on which Ed Koch can tell himself</p>
      <p begin="00:03:02,646" end="00:03:06,284">that the communities which are <br xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"/>being decimated by this epidemic</p>
      <p begin="00:03:06,284" end="00:03:09,521">are so weak and so divided <br xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"/>among themselves</p>
      <p begin="00:03:09,521" end="00:03:12,205">that he can keep serving us<br xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"/>this kind of bullshit.</p>
      <p begin="00:03:12,205" end="00:03:12,979">[laughter]</p>
      <p begin="00:03:13,042" end="00:03:15,723">Tomorrow morning, he will begin<br xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"/>to learn the truth.</p>
      <p begin="00:03:15,723" end="00:03:17,415">[applause]</p>
      <p begin="00:03:18,330" end="00:03:21,889">- [Female voice] ACT UP, stand tall<br xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"/>tomorrow morning at city hall.</p>
      <p begin="00:03:21,889" end="00:03:25,846">- [Crowd] ACT UP, stand tall<br xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"/>tomorrow morning at city hall.</p>
      <p begin="00:03:25,846" end="00:03:29,692">ACT UP, stand tall,<br xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"/>tomorrow morning at city hall.</p>
      <p begin="00:03:29,692" end="00:03:31,515">ACT UP, stand tall...</p>
      <p begin="00:03:31,515" end="00:03:35,133">&#9834; [Music] &#9834;</p>
      <p begin="00:03:39,728" end="00:03:41,784">$$ City Hall </p>
      <p begin="00:04:03,176" end="00:04:06,061">
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">- [male reporter] We're talking <br/>to Jim Eigo</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="00:04:06,061" end="00:04:09,161">
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">for the Treatment Issues Committee<br/>of ACT UP.</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="00:04:09,161" end="00:04:10,520">Jim, what specific treatment issues</p>
      <p begin="00:04:10,520" end="00:04:13,020">are pretty important <br xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"/>in this demonstration this week?</p>
      <p begin="00:04:13,020" end="00:04:16,390">
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">- [Jim Eigo] The municipal hospitals<br/>are totally falling apart.</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="00:04:16,390" end="00:04:19,309">
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">More than half the people<br/>who get diagnosed with AIDS today</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="00:04:19,309" end="00:04:22,691">
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">get diagnosed in the emergency rooms<br/>of our city.</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="00:04:22,691" end="00:04:24,826">You're going to find yourself <br xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"/>waiting four days</p>
      <p begin="00:04:24,826" end="00:04:27,676">in an emergency room before<br xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"/>you get a bed.</p>
      <p begin="00:04:27,946" end="00:04:31,936">- I'm pretty scared about being <br xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"/>HIV positive.</p>
      <p begin="00:04:31,990" end="00:04:33,578">I don't have much choice in the matter.</p>
      <p begin="00:04:33,578" end="00:04:34,801">- I just love all these people</p>
      <p begin="00:04:34,801" end="00:04:37,528">and I think that what we're <br xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"/>doing is really right.</p>
      <p begin="00:04:37,528" end="00:04:40,835">And -- I mean, listen to this <br xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"/>and look at our people,</p>
      <p begin="00:04:40,835" end="00:04:42,487">it's just really wonderful</p>
      <p begin="00:04:42,487" end="00:04:44,363">and it's worth putting<br xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"/><span tts:fontStyle="italic">ourselves on the line. </span></p>
      <p begin="00:04:44,363" end="00:04:46,576">- <span tts:fontStyle="italic">[Ann Northrop] There is<br/>no accurate diagnosis.</span></p>
      <p begin="00:04:46,576" end="00:04:48,537">
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">There are incentives<br/>in the city hospitals</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="00:04:48,537" end="00:04:50,560">
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">not to diagnose people with AIDS,</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="00:04:50,560" end="00:04:53,146">and therefore people don't get treated.</p>
      <p begin="00:04:53,146" end="00:04:56,556">We are angry at the way this city<br xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"/>has handled this crisis</p>
      <p begin="00:04:56,556" end="00:05:00,138">and we demand that Ed Koch<br xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"/>exert leadership</p>
      <p begin="00:05:00,138" end="00:05:02,720">and declare a state of emergency.</p>
      <p begin="00:05:02,743" end="00:05:04,128">[Applause]</p>
      <p begin="00:05:04,128" end="00:05:07,360">
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">- [Peter] Go on the street now or wait,<br/>those are the options.</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="00:05:07,360" end="00:05:08,987">One. He says go.</p>
      <p begin="00:05:08,987" end="00:05:09,997">
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">-Two, now.</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="00:05:09,997" end="00:05:11,157">-He says now, three.</p>
      <p begin="00:05:11,434" end="00:05:12,233">
        <br xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"/>
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">Don?</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="00:05:12,449" end="00:05:13,478">
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">Go now--</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="00:05:13,478" end="00:05:15,239">
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">-[Reporter] I'm standing here<br/>with Larry Kramer</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="00:05:15,293" end="00:05:17,672">
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">What is ACT UP trying to say today<br/>to Ed Koch?</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="00:05:17,672" end="00:05:19,890">-We're sending a message<br xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"/>to public officials,</p>
      <p begin="00:05:19,890" end="00:05:23,638">to closeted public officials<br xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"/>that we won't be shot down anymore</p>
      <p begin="00:05:23,638" end="00:05:25,538">and obviously all the AIDS issues.</p>
      <p begin="00:05:25,538" end="00:05:27,761">
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">-I would love to see, like,<br/>more cameras or something </span>
      </p>
      <p begin="00:05:27,761" end="00:05:29,522">you know, for our own protection.</p>
      <p begin="00:05:29,522" end="00:05:30,867">
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">-[male voice] and everyone here <br/>has concerns--</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="00:05:30,867" end="00:05:33,331">
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">-[Larry] People die everyday.<br/>Friends get sick everyday.</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="00:05:33,331" end="00:05:35,701">
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">I don't--it's like being in the trenches.</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="00:05:35,701" end="00:05:39,273">
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">There's such anger in the community<br/>and that it's coalescing in a way </span>
      </p>
      <p begin="00:05:39,273" end="00:05:41,757">that has never been done before.</p>
      <p begin="00:05:41,757" end="00:05:43,564">- Okay, which way do we face girlfriends?</p>
      <p begin="00:05:43,564" end="00:05:45,448">This way or that way?</p>
      <p begin="00:05:45,448" end="00:05:47,494">[crowd talking]</p>
      <p begin="00:05:49,517" end="00:05:51,480">[cars honking]<br xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"/>[crowd cheering and rallying]</p>
      <p begin="00:05:51,480" end="00:05:54,344">[together] HEALTHCARE IS A RIGHT.<br xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"/>HEALTHCARE IS A RIGHT.</p>
      <p begin="00:05:54,436" end="00:05:58,052">HEALTHCARE IS A RIGHT.<br xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"/>HEALTHCARE IS A RIGHT.</p>
      <p begin="00:05:58,052" end="00:06:01,543">HEALTHCARE IS A RIGHT.<br xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"/>HEALTHCARE IS A RIGHT.</p>
      <p begin="00:06:01,543" end="00:06:05,261">HEALTHCARE IS A RIGHT.<br xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"/>HEALTHCARE IS A RIGHT.</p>
      <p begin="00:06:05,304" end="00:06:07,280">- [police officer talking]</p>
      <p begin="00:06:07,295" end="00:06:11,724">[crowd shouting]</p>
      <p begin="00:06:14,549" end="00:06:16,789">&#9834; [music] &#9834;</p>
      <p begin="00:06:46,585" end="00:06:49,724">[crowd shouting]</p>
      <p begin="00:06:49,823" end="00:06:52,849">&#9834; [music] &#9834;</p>
      <p begin="00:07:15,513" end="00:07:18,500">$$ How To Survive A Plague. </p>
      <p begin="00:07:27,693" end="00:07:30,238">- I guess, I'm feeling pretty hopeless<br xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"/>at the moment.</p>
      <p begin="00:07:30,238" end="00:07:37,303">I think that the biggest question that<br xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"/>I'm facing now is how to remain hopeful</p>
      <p begin="00:07:37,303" end="00:07:40,229">in the face of increasing loss.</p>
      <p begin="00:07:40,659" end="00:07:43,456">- <span tts:fontStyle="italic">[David Barr] I don't know,<br/>maybe it sounds really corny </span></p>
      <p begin="00:07:43,456" end="00:07:44,302">but I--</p>
      <p begin="00:07:47,101" end="00:07:50,876">as difficult as the time is for us,</p>
      <p begin="00:07:52,594" end="00:07:59,950">I like being alive. And I love my friends <br xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"/>and I love my family.</p>
      <p begin="00:08:00,011" end="00:08:04,555"><span tts:fontStyle="italic">I love people around me.</span><br xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"/>- This, I'm gonna die from this.</p>
      <p begin="00:08:04,593" end="00:08:09,174">This isn't gonna be cured for<br xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"/>years and years and years and years.</p>
      <p begin="00:08:09,174" end="00:08:10,811">
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">- Doctor's office?</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="00:08:10,811" end="00:08:12,371">- [speaking in the phone] <br xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"/>Hi, it's Peter Staley.</p>
      <p begin="00:08:12,371" end="00:08:14,315">It's like living in a war.</p>
      <p begin="00:08:14,315" end="00:08:17,891">All around me,<br xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"/>friends are dropping dead.</p>
      <p begin="00:08:18,016" end="00:08:21,668">And you're scared for your own life<br xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"/>all at the same time.</p>
      <p begin="00:08:24,044" end="00:08:27,753">
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">I was diagnosed with AIDS-related complex</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="00:08:27,753" end="00:08:31,051">
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">while I was working as a bond trader<br/>on Wall Street.</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="00:08:31,359" end="00:08:33,190">
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">I had night sweats.</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="00:08:33,190" end="00:08:38,163">
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">I began to get dry, patchy, scaly,<br/>itchy skin on my face. </span>
      </p>
      <p begin="00:08:38,246" end="00:08:40,729">
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">And I would get sick constantly.</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="00:08:40,729" end="00:08:43,745">
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">Colds would lay me up for weeks.</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="00:08:44,323" end="00:08:48,053">I started to look around in desperation</p>
      <p begin="00:08:48,707" end="00:08:56,623">for ways that I could find treatments<br xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"/>to help save my life.</p>
      <p begin="00:08:59,392" end="00:09:04,375">And there was nothing coming out of our<br xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"/>government's efforts, I quickly realized.</p>
      <p begin="00:09:09,255" end="00:09:14,485">
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">Everything I read said I had about<br/>two years to live, at most. </span>
      </p>
      <p begin="00:09:16,639" end="00:09:19,951">[Crowd shouting]</p>
      <p begin="00:09:20,690" end="00:09:22,878">$$ ACT UPS first protest<br xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"/>March 24, 1987 </p>
      <p begin="00:09:22,878" end="00:09:24,734">
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">-[male voice] WHAT DO WE WANT?</span>
        <br xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"/>
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">-[crowd answering] A CURE!</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="00:09:24,734" end="00:09:26,791">
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">-[male voice] WHEN DO WE WANT IT?</span>
        <br xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"/>
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">-[crowd answering] NOW!</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="00:09:26,791" end="00:09:29,223">
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">-[Peter] I was on my way to work</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="00:09:29,233" end="00:09:32,274">
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">and I got handed <br/>a flier about ACT UP and AIDS.</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="00:09:32,284" end="00:09:36,490">
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">My mentor says, "If you ask me,<br/>I think they all deserve to die" </span>
      </p>
      <p begin="00:09:36,490" end="00:09:38,511">
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">"because they took it up their butt."</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="00:09:38,770" end="00:09:43,850">
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">I was deeply closeted and I had to just <br/>stew about it for the rest of the day.</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="00:09:46,726" end="00:09:49,562">
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">I got myself to the very next <br/>ACT UP meeting.</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="00:09:49,675" end="00:09:53,132">
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">They could just tap into that<br/>immediate anger and get stuff done.</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="00:09:53,132" end="00:09:55,702">
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">-[female voice] We need to get approval <br/>on this...</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="00:09:55,702" end="00:09:59,208">
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">This is a non-violent <br/>and quiet kiss-in.</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="00:09:59,208" end="00:10:02,117">We will not leave until<br xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"/>the administrator meets with us</p>
      <p begin="00:10:02,117" end="00:10:07,024">and tells us that Saint Vincent's<br xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"/>is willing to make a public statement</p>
      <p begin="00:10:07,024" end="00:10:09,274">condemning gay and lesbian violence.</p>
      <p begin="00:10:09,274" end="00:10:12,243">[crowd cheering and applauding]</p>
      <p begin="00:10:15,282" end="00:10:17,289">- All those in favor?</p>
      <p begin="00:10:19,023" end="00:10:21,137">
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">-All those oppose?</span>
      </p>
