      <p begin="01:43:11,846" end="01:43:14,378">- <span tts:fontStyle="italic">[Peter] I'd like to close <br/>with words written</span></p>
      <p begin="01:43:14,378" end="01:43:16,378">
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">by fellow AIDS activist, Peter Russo.</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="01:43:16,734" end="01:43:20,892">
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">When the future generations ask<br/>what we did in the war, </span>
      </p>
      <p begin="01:43:21,061" end="01:43:25,035">
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">We have to be able to tell them<br/>that we were out here fighting. </span>
      </p>
      <p begin="01:43:25,831" end="01:43:27,136">And we have to leave a legacy</p>
      <p begin="01:43:27,136" end="01:43:30,457">to the generations<br xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"/>of people who will come after us.</p>
      <p begin="01:43:30,457" end="01:43:35,071">Remember that someday,<br xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"/>the AIDS crisis will be over.</p>
      <p begin="01:43:35,776" end="01:43:38,379">And when that day has come and gone,</p>
      <p begin="01:43:38,379" end="01:43:40,727">there will be a people <br xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"/>alive on this earth,</p>
      <p begin="01:43:40,727" end="01:43:44,582">gay people and straight people,<br xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"/>black people and white people,</p>
      <p begin="01:43:44,582" end="01:43:48,128">men and women, who will hear the story,</p>
      <p begin="01:43:48,190" end="01:43:51,150">that once, there was a terrible disease,</p>
      <p begin="01:43:51,150" end="01:43:54,711">and that a brave group of people<br xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"/>stood up and fought,</p>
      <p begin="01:43:54,711" end="01:43:59,145">and in some cases died, so that<br xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"/>others might live and be free.</p>
      <p begin="01:44:00,869" end="01:44:02,522">&#9834; [music] &#9834;</p>
      <p begin="01:44:02,522" end="01:44:06,901">$$ The number of people who die<br xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"/>because they can't afford AIDS drugs: </p>
      <p begin="01:44:06,901" end="01:44:09,290">$$ 2,000,000 every year<br xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"/>5,000 every day, 4 every minute </p>
      <p begin="01:44:09,290" end="01:44:09,290">$$ ACT UP END AIDS. </p>
      <p begin="01:44:18,658" end="01:44:21,026">- [Peter talking]</p>
      <p begin="01:44:43,409" end="01:44:45,734">- Ouch! That hurts!</p>
      <p begin="01:44:52,606" end="01:44:55,709">- Our information is essential<br xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"/>so that doctors and patients</p>
      <p begin="01:44:55,709" end="01:44:58,260">can make intelligent treatments.</p>
      <p begin="01:45:01,177" end="01:45:02,277">- <span tts:fontStyle="italic">Okay. </span><br xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"/>- Alright.</p>
      <p begin="01:45:02,277" end="01:45:03,853">- [male talking]</p>
      <p begin="01:45:03,853" end="01:45:06,175">- No, I won't take that.</p>
      <p begin="01:45:06,175" end="01:45:09,445">- I'm really glad to see everybody here.<br xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"/>You look really good.</p>
      <p begin="01:45:14,317" end="01:45:17,178">- I'd like to suggest <br xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"/>that we not be unethical</p>
      <p begin="01:45:17,178" end="01:45:20,731">to do a randomized trial<br xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"/>on two different prevention programs.</p>
      <p begin="01:45:23,255" end="01:45:27,064">- If we don't eradicate HIV everywhere<br xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"/>we will never eradicate it anywhere.</p>
      <p begin="01:45:32,832" end="01:45:36,933">- We may march without incident<br xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"/>or they may arrest us,</p>
      <p begin="01:45:36,933" end="01:45:38,656">but it'll all be fun.</p>
      <p begin="01:45:42,302" end="01:45:46,541">- [male talking]</p>
      <p begin="01:45:50,325" end="01:45:53,365">- We're going to end it today.</p>
      <p begin="01:45:55,555" end="01:46:00,976">&#9834; [music] &#9834;</p>
      <p begin="01:46:12,458" end="01:46:19,033">- In just over two years, that drug<br xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"/>went from test tube to full approval.</p>
      <p begin="01:46:22,222" end="01:46:26,173">[applause]</p>
      <p begin="01:46:29,438" end="01:46:33,759">&#9834; [music] &#9834;</p>
